            . I am the wife of Thomas Hall, a <rs id="t18270913-322-viclabel1794" type="occupation">linen-draper</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18270913-322-victim2405 t18270913-322-viclabel1794"></join>, of <placeName id="t18270913-322-crimeloc1795">Bishopsgate-street</placeName>
